			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000001"]
			description: ["The Map Creator is crafted from paper and redstone dust and produces a single Common Dungeon Map when used. Common maps run Tier 0–10 content — the entry tier. Higher tier maps are found only inside Reward Rooms; you cannot craft them. Craft a Map Creator before you reach level 55 so you have a starting map ready when the content becomes accessible. The map_creator item is consumed on use and produces one dungeon_map."]
			id: "DG01000000000002"
