		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000003"]
			description: ["Dungeon Realm generates a randomized instanced dungeon when you activate the Map Device. Kill percentage tracks how many dungeon mobs you have eliminated — higher percentage increases the quality of loot in the Reward Room at the end. Uncommon exploration unlocks at certain thresholds; Rare and Epic unlock at higher ones. Explore every room before triggering the Boss Teleporter. Rushing the boss immediately gives you the lowest reward tier."]
			id: "DG01000000000004"
			rewards: [
				{
