		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000001"]
			description: ["Library of Exile adds a portal system built from Portal Frame blocks. Assemble the frame structure, then use an atlas map on it to open a connection to a Library of Exile instance. Library of Exile operates as a parallel mapping system to Dungeon Realm — different map pool, different boss roster, different loot tables. The two systems do not share progress. Build the Library portal as a second dungeon entry point once you have the Dungeon Realm system running."]
			id: "DG01000000000008"
