		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000008"]
			description: ["Dungeon Maps and Library of Exile atlas maps both roll random affixes when generated. Player affixes reduce your resistances, slow movement, or cut healing. Mob affixes increase health, add elemental damage types, or raise movement speed. A map with heavy affixes is significantly harder — but yields substantially better loot on completion. Some affixes can be rerolled using currency items before entering. High-affix maps that you can clear are the most efficient way to gear up."]
			id: "DG01000000000009"
