			x: -5.0d
			y: -5.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000001"]
			description: ["Ancient Obelisks are structure blocks that spawn in the overworld. Right-clicking an Obelisk with an Obelisk Map triggers a wave-based encounter at that location — no separate dimension, no map device needed. Mobs spawn in waves at the obelisk site and scale to your Mine and Slash character level. Completing all waves yields obelisk-tier loot drops. Obelisk Maps are found in chests and structures worldwide, and can also be crafted. Obelisks provide a dimension-free alternative to map running for early dungeon content."]
			id: "DG01000000000010"
