			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["DG01000000000010"]
			description: ["Obelisk Maps roll affixes just like Dungeon Maps — mob health, elemental damage, player stat reductions. A high-affix Obelisk encounter at your character level is a meaningful combat test without the overhead of portal construction or map device management. Use Obelisks as a fast, accessible source of Mine and Slash gear drops at mid-game before you have a full map-running setup established. Each Obelisk can be activated repeatedly with different maps."]
			id: "DG01000000000011"
