			description: ["Maps run. Portals opened. Waves cleared. Bosses killed. The dungeon systems in this pack form a fully independent progression arc that sits on top of the Mine and Slash gear loop: Dungeon Realm for instanced map runs, Library of Exile for atlas alternates, Ancient Obelisks for wave encounters, The Harvest for Chaotic Gem farming. Each system feeds into the next. The Master Delver has run them all — and the Uber Bosses still wait at the top."]
